Silp 1
Q. 1) Write a PHP script to keep track of number of times the web page has been accessed (Use Session 
Tracking )
Sol: 
<html>
<head>
<title> Number of times the web page has been viited.</title>
</head>
<body>
<?php
session_start();
if(isset($_SESSION['count']))
$_SESSION['count']=$_SESSION['count']+1;
else
$_SESSION['count']=1;
echo "<h3>This page is accessed</h3>".$_SESSION['count'];
?>
</body>
</html> 
